cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.DC, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a covert channel in data center networks, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper discusses privacy threats and information leakage, which are related to cryptography and security. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper computes the capacity of the covert channel, which is related to information theory. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper discusses a covert channel in shared resources, which is related to distributed computing. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper presents a system model and analyzes the effect of other users on the information transmission rate, which is related to systems and control.
